### 1) Get Apple developer token (backend generated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/music/developer-token
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 2) Connect Apple Music account (save musicUserToken for current user)
POST {{baseUrl}}/music/connect
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "musicUserToken": "{{musicUserToken}}"
}

### 3) Trigger discovery sync from Apple Music data
POST {{baseUrl}}/discovery/music/sync
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 4) Fetch top artists (profile)
GET {{baseUrl}}/music/top-artists
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 5) Fetch top tracks / songs (profile)
GET {{baseUrl}}/music/top-tracks
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 6) Fetch top albums (profile)
GET {{baseUrl}}/music/top-albums
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 7) Fetch currently playing (returns 204 when none)
GET {{baseUrl}}/music/currently-playing
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 8) Disconnect Apple Music account
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/music/disconnect
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Accept: application/json
